Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不会有任何人来打扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟哎哟！你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饿狼吗？自那之后我可真是太想见你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你最好赶紧逃跑 虎心王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太让我兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以柔克刚是你的绝技吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…看透你的伎俩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露妮！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军师！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个就是你哦 母狼
